# A simple unit cube centered at origin
v -10.0 -10.0 -10.0
v  10.0 -10.0 -10.0
v  10.0  10.0 -10.0
v -10.0  10.0 -10.0
v -10.0 -10.0  10.0
v  10.0 -10.0  10.0
v  10.0  10.0  10.0
v -10.0  10.0  10.0

# Each face is a quad — should fan-triangulate to 12 triangles total
f 1 2 3 4
f 5 8 7 6
f 1 5 6 2
f 2 6 7 3
f 3 7 8 4
f 4 8 5 1
